  "text": "An interesting overview for other metrics which can be applied to mosaic comparison is given in [CITATION_1] . The author discusses several dissimilarity measures which can be applied to better describe achieved results: figure of merit (FOM), Yasnoff distance and also introduces his own measure, which we call Gavet. In these formulas B is assumed to be a perfect solution, while A is the mask prepared in the research.",
